      "updated": 1775926637752,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "➙ recv: health-check endpoint, global ACL checks, basic normalizations, \n          route selection, route preflight, etc.\n➙ hit/miss/pass: debug headers\n➙ pipe: WebSocket upgrades\n➙ deliver/synth: error handling, debug headers, etc.\n➙ backend_fetch: request cleanup, ESI announcement, etc.\n➙ backend_response: TTL, grace, keep & ESI initialization, Cache-Control\n                           parsing, X-Varnish-* parsing, etc.\n",
      "fontSize": 20.138669866184937,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "➙ recv: health-check endpoint, global ACL checks, basic normalizations, \n          route selection, route preflight, etc.\n➙ hit/miss/pass: debug headers\n➙ pipe: WebSocket upgrades\n➙ deliver/synth: error handling, debug headers, etc.\n➙ backend_fetch: request cleanup, ESI announcement, etc.\n➙ backend_response: TTL, grace, keep & ESI initialization, Cache-Control\n                           parsing, X-Varnish-* parsing, etc.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
