      "updated": 1776164553905,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "➙ recv: HTTPS redirections, invalidations, store PUT/POST body, return\n          pipe/pass/hash, etc.\n➙ hash: hash PUT/POST body, custom URL/host hashing\n➙ hit/miss: invalidations\n➙ deliver: debug headers, response cleanup, ESI & IMS/INM, counters\n➙ synth: counters\n➙ backend_response: backend name logging, counters, TTL/grace/keep\n                           limits, lurker-friendly bans, registration of Ykeys, \n                           HFM vs. HFP, etc.\n➙ backend_error: backend name logging, retry requests, revive objects  \n",
      "fontSize": 20.138669866184937,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "➙ recv: HTTPS redirections, invalidations, store PUT/POST body, return\n          pipe/pass/hash, etc.\n➙ hash: hash PUT/POST body, custom URL/host hashing\n➙ hit/miss: invalidations\n➙ deliver: debug headers, response cleanup, ESI & IMS/INM, counters\n➙ synth: counters\n➙ backend_response: backend name logging, counters, TTL/grace/keep\n                           limits, lurker-friendly bans, registration of Ykeys, \n                           HFM vs. HFP, etc.\n➙ backend_error: backend name logging, retry requests, revive objects  \n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
