      "seed": 1012693813,
      "version": 759,
      "versionNonce": 1929736245,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775926637753,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "➙ recv: client IP extraction & server name logging\n➙ backend_fetch: server name logging\n\n➙ environment.vcl: environment-specific context & objects\n➙ replication-*.vcl: cache replication strategy to be used\n➙ akamai.vcl: optional Akamai integration\n➙ acls.vcl: global ACLs\n➙ backends.vcl: global probes & static backends\n➙ config.vcl: global settings, directors & counters, etc.\n➙ helpers.vcl: global helpers  ",
      "fontSize": 20.138669866184937,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "➙ recv: client IP extraction & server name logging\n➙ backend_fetch: server name logging\n\n➙ environment.vcl: environment-specific context & objects\n➙ replication-*.vcl: cache replication strategy to be used\n➙ akamai.vcl: optional Akamai integration\n➙ acls.vcl: global ACLs\n➙ backends.vcl: global probes & static backends\n➙ config.vcl: global settings, directors & counters, etc.\n➙ helpers.vcl: global helpers  ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
